<h1 style="background: #1b4cbc2e; padding: 4px;">Fair Usage Policy</h1>
<p>Prochatr&rsquo;s fair usage policy (&ldquo;FUP&rdquo;) is designed to prevent fraud and abuse of our products. Prochatr&rsquo;s products are for individual use only in accordance with the Agreement and this FUP (&ldquo;Legitimate Use&rdquo;).</p>
